The paper deals with mechanism design for purchasing private data, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves privacy concerns and differential privacy, which are topics in cryptography (cs.CR) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses accuracy and monotonicity, which are concepts in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG).
